Package org.apache.drill.exec Description

Drill execution engine, including: physical operators, runtime code generation, planning, RPC layer, Value Vector data structures. The Drill execution engine is a distributed query system, designed primarily for running interactive SQL queries on Big Data. For more information see the project architecture page on the wiki @See Drill Architecture
